13 - Lifted (2006)





TECHNICAL DATA:

All the shorts are 1080p, using x264 video codec and AC3 for audio. About quality, I choosed to encode using level 18 constant quantizer, that is generally considered the best quality you can achieve with x264 codec. When avaliable there are also subtitles and foreign languages (French, German, Italian). Every short, except for &quot;Jack-Jack Attack&quot;, has also an english-commentary audio track, that describes the difficulties faced for the accomplishment.


